			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">[...] <persName ref="p8110" cert="high">Velsius</persName> ad nos non venit; quo abierit, nescio.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cur non patribus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinis</placeName> suam offert prophetiam?</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Apud nos satis recte omnia habent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> nihil audimus nisi fausta de progressu evangelii [...].</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName>, 15. iulii 61.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8018" cert="high">I. Hall.</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
